descriptionHtml:
🏡 Are you good at house cleaning?🔨

Try out different concept furniture and clean in this exciting renovation game.🧩
😀 Get into the satisfying world of cleaning and cure your OCD！😀
descriptionShort: A casual game to clean and renovate the room. Make the messy house tidy!
